    Wrangling Function

    get_cleanschedule_met.Rd

    A function that cleans the output (data rame) extracted from the webscrape_sports function. This function maps the MET values into the data in order to calculate the calorie burn amount per activity.

    Usage

    get_cleanschedule_met(sport_schedule, met_values)

    Arguments

    sport_schedule

    Data frame containing the sports schedule of the number of days selected obtained when running webscrape_sports function

    met_values

    Data frame containing the MET values per sport activity obtained when running webscrape_MET function.

    Value

    A data frame containing the activities per day with their correspondingly Met values.
